OL,3,CEx-soldier says women in Army treated
OL,4,Clike 'meat in a tank of sharks'
OL,6,FTamzin Hort told ITV News she would
OL,7,Fadvise women against joining the Army,
OL,8,Fsaying that if people were shown what
OL,9,Fit was really like, "they'd have no
OL,10,Fone"
OL,12,FA friend and former colleague of
OL,13,Fteenage soldier Jaysley Beck has
OL,14,Fdescribed being a woman in the force
OL,15,Fas the same as being a "goldfish or a
OL,16,Fpiece of meat in a tank of sharks".
OL,18,FRoyal Artillery Gunner Beck was found
OL,19,Fdead in her room at Larkhill Camp in
OL,20,FWiltshire on December 15, 2021.
