OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News, Tamzin
OL,7,FHort - who has since left the Army -
OL,8,Fsaid it was a "man's world" where
OL,9,Fwomen are the target of misogynistic
OL,10,Fand inappropriate behaviour.
OL,12,FShe claims abuse is ongoing and called
OL,13,Ffor the civilian police to have
OL,14,Foversight over issues reported by
OL,15,Fservice personnel, rather than the
OL,16,Fmilitary police, in order to improve
OL,17,Fthe complaints process and encourage
OL,18,Fpeople to come forward.
