OL,6,FMs Hort, who joined the Army when she
OL,7,Fwas 17, told ITV News of the misogyny
OL,8,Fand inappropriate behaviour she and
OL,9,Fother women experienced, adding that
OL,10,Fthis type of behaviour was happening
OL,11,Fin plain sight.
OL,13,F"They see girls either as you sleep
OL,14,Fwith everyone or you're a lesbian, or
OL,15,Fif you're in between you're a
OL,16,Fchallenge - they'll terrorise you
OL,17,Funtil you can get somewhere.
OL,19,F"You'd get comments like, 'oh you're
OL,20,Fgood looking' and 'come to my room,
OL,21,Fcome to my room'".
