OL,8,F"slag", comments which she said start
OL,9,F"getting in your head".
OL,11,FShe added that "people just get
OL,12,Fsexually assaulted left, right and
OL,13,Fcentre and nothing's done about it"
OL,14,Fand claimed "the men are all
OL,15,Fmisogynists" in the Army.
