OL,6,FWhen asked if she thought this
OL,7,Fbehaviour was happening in plain
OL,8,Fsight, Ms Hort said: "Yeah. I've been
OL,9,Fin situations where I've been
OL,10,Fdownstairs with everyone while they're
OL,11,Fall socialising and someone's just
OL,12,Fhappily just smacked my bum."
OL,14,FDespite loving her job, Ms Hort said
OL,15,Fshe left the Army because of "the
OL,16,Fpeople, the constant putting you down,
OL,17,Fthe constant name calls, the constant
OL,18,Funwanted attention".
OL,20,F"If I've said no, it means no," she
OL,21,Fcontinued.
