OL,6,FDespite not being aware of what Gunner
OL,7,FBeck was going through, Ms Hort said
OL,8,Fif she had spoken out, "no one could
OL,9,Fhave helped her" because reporting
OL,10,Fbehaviour meant "she'd be known as a
OL,11,Fgrass" or "an attention seeker."
OL,13,FMs Hort's comments came as an inquest
OL,14,Fconcluded that "on the balance of
OL,15,Fprobabilities", the Army's handling of
OL,16,Fa sexual assault complaint made by
OL,17,FGunner Beck "played more than a
OL,18,Fminimal contributory part in her
OL,19,Fdeath".
