OL,6,FThe inquest heard that in July 2021
OL,7,Fshe complained that she had been
OL,8,Fsexually assaulted by a senior
OL,9,Fcolleague during a stay at Thorney
OL,10,FIsland.
OL,12,FBattery Sergeant Major Michael Webber,
OL,13,Fnow of Warrant Officer 2 rank, was
OL,14,Fgiven a "minor sanction" for his
OL,15,Factions.
OL,17,FThe coroner said this incident "should
OL,18,Fhave been reported to police and the
OL,19,Ffailure to do so breached Army policy".
