OL,6,FThe inquest also heard the 19-year-old
OL,7,Fhad complained to her family about the
OL,8,F"possessive and psychotic" behaviour
OL,9,Fof her boss, Ryan Mason, a bombardier
OL,10,Fat the time.
OL,12,FThe hearing was told the senior
OL,13,Fsoldier, who had mental health issues
OL,14,Fand had previously self-harmed, had
OL,15,Fsent Gunner Beck more than 1,000
OL,16,Fmessages in October 2021 and 3,600 in
OL,17,FNovember, and had spoken of his love
OL,18,Ffor her.
