OL,6,FGunner Beck's mother said her daughter
OL,7,F"did not feel safe" as Mr Mason's
OL,8,Fbehaviour intensified, and the
OL,9,Fteenager feared he had hacked her
OL,10,Fphone and was watching her.
OL,12,FMr Mason denied this and the coroner
OL,13,Ffound it "unlikely" that he was
OL,14,Ftracking her.
OL,16,FAn Army service inquiry report
OL,17,Fpublished in October 2023 described
OL,18,Fthis as "an intense period of
OL,19,Funwelcome behaviour", and said it was
OL,20,F"almost certain this was a causal
OL,21,Ffactor" in her death.
